-- QBE to Assume Balboa Insurance Liabilities of $1.2 Billion
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   R i c h a r d s
-- 2011-02-03T23:01:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-03/qbe-will-assume-1-2-billion-of-bofa-balboa-unit-s-insurance-liabilities.html
  QBE Insurance Group Ltd . said it will
assume the insurance liabilities of Balboa and its affiliates of
about $1.2 billion matched by tangible assets of an equivalent
amount, according to a regulatory statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Richards at 
 vrichards@bloomberg.net  